I am never watching Family Matters again. Anyway I found something kind of peculiar.
1 Karin x Tsunade by ~zakuta on deviantART I am not sure what to make of this. The fact I find it arousing is even more disturbing. I don;t think I want to know what was going through this artist's mind at the time.

Hiiiiiiiiiiiiiiiiiiiiiiiiiiiiiiiiiiii

And I have found the loveliest, most fascinating, hippest thing out there!


<lj-embed id="1" />

IT'S CALCULICIOUS!

Like IIIIIiiiiiiiiiiiiiiiiiiiii aaaaaaaaaam! 8B

It looks like I have a little bit of free time this evening. Why don't I take a few sketch requests? I doodled this the other day f you are curious about my level of skill (or lack thereof, I never said I take pride in being an artist): I will be willing to take up to five requests. I'm sorry, but I just do not have the time to do any more than that. And to my former teammates, I already know your opinion of my skills. Don't even bother commenting, it would just be a waste of your time and mine.
More ninja seem to have discovered this than I expected. Interesting. However, there seem to be quite many others who I do not recognize. Doubly interesting.
